Interface LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    OUT - the output data type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    com.github.dm.jrt.channel.Channel, com.github.dm.jrt.channel.Channel.OutputChannel<OUT>, com.github.dm.jrt.builder.ConfigurableBuilder<com.github.dm.jrt.stream.StreamChannel<OUT>>, Iterable<OUT>, Iterator<OUT>, com.github.dm.jrt.android.builder.LoaderConfigurableBuilder<LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>>, com.github.dm.jrt.stream.StreamChannel<OUT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultLoaderStreamChannelCompat

    public interface LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>
extends com.github.dm.jrt.stream.StreamChannel<OUT>, com.github.dm.jrt.android.builder.LoaderConfigurableBuilder<LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>>
    Interface defining a stream output channel, that is, a channel concatenating map and reduce functions, employing Android loaders to run the backing routines.
    In fact, each function in the channel is backed by a routine instance, that can have its own specific configuration and invocation mode.
    In order to prevent undesired leaks, the class of the specified functions must have a static scope.

    Note that, if at least one reduce function is part of the concatenation, the results will be propagated only when the previous routine invocations complete.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 01/15/2016.

      • withLoaders

        @NotNull
com.github.dm.jrt.android.builder.LoaderConfiguration.Builder<? extends LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>> withLoaders()
        Gets the loader configuration builder related only to the next concatenated routine instance. Any further addition to the chain will retain only the stream configuration.
        Only the options set in this configuration (that is, the ones with a value different from the default) will override the stream one.

        Note that the configuration builder will be initialized with the current configuration for the next routine.

        Specified by:
        withLoaders in interface com.github.dm.jrt.android.builder.LoaderConfigurableBuilder<LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>>
        Returns:
        the invocation configuration builder.

      • withStreamLoaders

        @NotNull
com.github.dm.jrt.android.builder.LoaderConfiguration.Builder<? extends LoaderStreamChannelCompat<OUT>> withStreamLoaders()
        Gets the loader configuration builder related to the whole stream.
        The configuration options will be applied to all the next concatenated routine unless overwritten by specific ones.

        Note that the configuration builder will be initialized with the current stream configuration.

        Returns:
        the invocation configuration builder.
